1.说明
   phone为手机号
   gatewayid 为主机id  通过udp组播获取
   num 为房间第几设备 1 2 3 4 
2. 灯
  2.1 订阅 gatewayid/light/num   
  2.2 发布 phone/light/num 
  2.3 发送
       {
	     "power": "off/on",
	     "number": 1/2/3
       }
	   说明 "number": 对应房间灯序列
  2.4 返回结果
       {
	     "power": "off/on",
	     "number": 1/2/3
       }
	   
	   
	   
3. 护理床
  3.1 订阅 gatewayid/nuringbed/num    
  3.2 发布 phone/nuringbed/num   
  3.3 发送
       {
	    "hexArry": [0,255,64,191]
       }
	   说明 "hexArry" 四个字节数组，包括护理床10种控制命令
	   
  3.4 返回结果
       {
	     "hexArry": [0,255,64,191]
       }
	   
	   
	   
4. 红外转发器
  4.1 订阅 gatewayid/irdevice/num    
  4.2 发布 phone/irdevice/num   
  4.3 发送/控制设备
    {
       "device": "tv/aircondition",
	   "key_name" "温度+/-等",
	   "ircode_length": 21,
	   "ircode": [131,6,4,146,0,4,128,0,0,0,96,128,92,174,0,37,0,0,48,20,1]
	}
	说明 "ircode_length" 红外码长度，"ircode" 红外码
  4.4 返回控制结果
     {
       "device": "tv/aircondition",
	   "key_name" "温度+/-等",
	   "state": "ok/error"
	 }
  
  4.5 发送/学习按键
	 {
	   "device": "tv/aircondition",
	   "key_name" "温度+/-等"
	   "learn_mode": "on/off"
	 }
  4.6 返回/学习按键 
	 {
       "device": "tv/aircondition",
	   "key_name" "温度+/-等",
	   "ircode_length": 21,
	   "ircode": [131,6,4,146,0,4,128,0,0,0,96,128,92,174,0,37,0,0,48,20,1]
	 }
	 
	 学习完后需要关闭学习状态
  